Step 10: Using PWABuilder

Go to PWABuilder.com

Visit https://www.pwabuilder.com


Enter your URL

Input your deployed HTTPS URL
Click "Start"


Review Report Card

Fix any issues flagged
Ensure all PWA criteria are met


Package for Android

Click "Package for Store"
Select "Android"
Choose "Google Play"


Configure Android Options:

   Package ID: com.constructioncalc.app
   App Name: Construction Calculator Pro
   Version: 1.0.0
   Version Code: 1
   Launcher Name: ConstCalc
   Theme Color: #f97316
   Background Color: #ffffff
   Icon URL: [Your 512x512 icon URL]
   Signing Key: Generate new

Add Google Play Billing:

Enable "In-app Purchases"
Product ID: pro_version
Product Type: One-time purchase
Price: $4.99


Download Package

Click "Generate"
Download the .aab file
Download signing key (keep safe!)




Step 11: Google Play Console Setup
A. Create App Listing

Go to Google Play Console

https://play.google.com/console


Create Application

Click "Create app"
Name: Construction Calculator Pro
Default language: English
App or game: App
Free or paid: Free


Add In-App Products

Navigate to: Monetize > Products > In-app products
Click "Create product"
Product ID: pro_version
Name: Pro Version
Description: Unlock all professional construction tools
Status: Active
Price: $4.99



