Step 13: Testing Before Launch
Test on Android Device:
bash# Install ADB
# Connect Android device

# Install the APK (from PWABuilder test build)
adb install construction-calculator.apk

# Test purchases in sandbox mode
# Add test account in Play Console
Test Checklist:

 App installs correctly
 All calculators work offline
 Cement calculator works (free)
 Pro features show overlay
 Purchase flow works
 Pro features unlock after purchase
 App icon displays correctly
 Splash screen shows
 No console errors


